&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; to change in the near future as financial institutions continue to incur significant losses to remediate customer fraud resulting from data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=6c3deb36-5832-4e2c-80a0-c25f97d39a9a&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=6c3deb36-5832-4e2c-80a0-c25f97d39a9a&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Ensuring Patient Concerns Don&amp;rsquo;t Limit Health Data Exchange&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In fact, the most common reason for highly publicized data breaches in health care is not malicious hacking, but health care providers&amp;rsquo; bad data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://ehrintelligence.com/news/ensuring-patient-concerns-dont-limit-health-data-exchange&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://ehrintelligence.com/news/ensuring-patient-concerns-dont-limit-health-data-exchange&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;New Law to Strengthen Data Protection Policies in Chile&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Latin America is particularly sensitive to data breaches due to the lack of legislative initiative in the region. According to Privacy and Data Protection &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.leadersleague.com/en/news/new-law-to-strengthen-data-protection-policies-in-chile&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.leadersleague.com/en/news/new-law-to-strengthen-data-protection-policies-in-chile&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

